Skills system implemented per Anthropic skills.md format. Skills are folders with SKILL.md files. Agents have a skills: [] field in YAML config. Only listed skill names+descriptions appear in the system prompt — full content loaded on demand via read_skill MCP tool. Built-in skill: build-app (teaches agents the create_app_workspace → publish_app workflow). Key: agents must have 'build-app' in their skills list to see it.
